INSERT INTO `attraction_metadata` VALUES (89,232,'{\"email\": {\"url\": \"mailto:enquiries@mandai.com\", \"value\": \"enquiries@mandai.com\"}, \"phone\": {\"url\": \"tel:+6562693411\", \"value\": \"+65 6269 3411\"}, \"website\": {\"url\": \"https://www.mandai.com/en/singapore-zoo.html\", \"value\": \"www.mandai.com/en/singapore-zoo.html\"}}','The Singapore Zoo is wheelchair accessible, with ramps and elevators available in many areas. Accessible restrooms are located throughout the park. Wheelchairs are available for rent.','February to April (drier season)','[{\"day\": \"Monday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"08:30\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Tuesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"08:30\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Wednesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"08:30\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Thursday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"08:30\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Friday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"08:30\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Saturday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"08:30\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Sunday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"08:30\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}]','The Singapore Zoo is a world-renowned wildlife park known for its \'open concept\' enclosures. Home to a diverse range of animals in naturalistic habitats, it offers immersive and educational experiences for visitors of all ages. It is part of Mandai Wildlife Reserve.',240,'[\"Observe the orangutans in their free-ranging habitat.\", \"Visit the fragile forest to see sloths, lemurs and other unique species.\", \"Explore the Reptile Garden and see a variety of snakes, lizards, and turtles.\", \"Attend the \'Rainforest Fights Back\' show to learn about rainforest conservation.\", \"Take the tram ride for a quick overview of the zoo.\", \"Have breakfast with the orangutans (pre-booking required).\", \"Discover the Australian Outback zone and spot kangaroos and wallabies.\", \"Watch the playful sea lions during the sea lion show.\"]','2025-12-15 17:52:49','2025-12-15 17:52:49'),(90,233,'{\"email\": {\"url\": \"mailto:enquiries@marinabaysands.com\", \"value\": \"enquiries@marinabaysands.com\"}, \"phone\": {\"url\": \"tel:+6566888826\", \"value\": \"+65 6688 8826\"}, \"website\": {\"url\": \"https://www.marinabaysands.com/attractions/sands-skypark.html/?utm_source=google&utm_medium=GMB&utm_campaign=skypark_info_main\", \"value\": \"www.marinabaysands.com/attractions/sands-skypark.html/?utm_source=google&utm_medium=GMB&utm_campaign=skypark_info_main\"}}','The SkyPark Observation Deck is wheelchair accessible, with elevators providing access to all levels. Accessible restrooms are available on site, and staff are available to assist visitors with disabilities.','Year-round, but avoiding peak hours during weekends and public holidays is recommended for a less crowded experience.','[{\"day\": \"Monday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"17:00\", \"close_time\": \"22:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Tuesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"17:00\", \"close_time\": \"22:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Wednesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"17:00\", \"close_time\": \"22:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Thursday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"17:00\", \"close_time\": \"22:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Friday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"17:00\", \"close_time\": \"22:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Saturday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"17:00\", \"close_time\": \"22:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Sunday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"17:00\", \"close_time\": \"22:00\"}]','The SkyPark Observation Deck offers unparalleled panoramic views of Singapore\'s skyline. Perched atop the iconic Marina Bay Sands, it\'s a must-visit for breathtaking vistas. Capture stunning photos and soak in the vibrant city.',60,'[\"Spectacular 360-degree views of Singapore\'s skyline and Marina Bay\", \"Photo opportunities with iconic landmarks like Gardens by the Bay and the Singapore Flyer\", \"Enjoy the breeze and open-air setting at 57 stories above the ground\", \"Capture stunning sunset views over the city (weather permitting)\", \"Observe the bustling activity of the Singapore Strait\", \"Spot interesting architectural landmarks and urban planning features\", \"Learn about Singapore\'s history and development through the scenery\", \"Relax and enjoy the ambiance of the observation deck\"]','2025-12-15 17:52:56','2025-12-15 17:52:56'),(91,234,'{\"email\": {\"url\": \"mailto:guestrelations@skylineluge.com\", \"value\": \"guestrelations@skylineluge.com\"}, \"phone\": {\"url\": \"tel:+6562740472\", \"value\": \"+65 6274 0472\"}, \"website\": {\"url\": \"https://sentosa.skylineluge.com/?utm_source=gmb_listing&utm_medium=organic\", \"value\": \"sentosa.skylineluge.com/?utm_source=gmb_listing&utm_medium=organic\"}}','Skyline Luge Sentosa offers accessible options. The Skyride provides wheelchair access, and there are designated wheelchair-friendly Luge carts available. Staff assistance is provided for boarding and disembarking; however, independent maneuvering may be required.','Year-round, but early mornings or late afternoons avoid peak heat and crowds. Weekdays are generally less crowded than weekends.','[{\"day\": \"Monday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"19:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Tuesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"19:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Wednesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"19:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Thursday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"19:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Friday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"21:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Saturday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"21:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Sunday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"19:30\"}]','Skyline Luge Sentosa offers a unique part-go kart, part-toboggan ride experience. Navigate downhill tracks with control over speed and steering. Enjoy scenic views from the Skyride chairlift back to the top.',90,'[\"Ride the Luge down four unique tracks: Dragon, Jungle, Expedition, and Kupu-Kupu.\", \"Enjoy panoramic views of Sentosa Island and the Singapore skyline from the Skyride.\", \"Experience the thrill of controlling your own descent on the Luge.\", \"Take the Skyride at night for a mesmerizing view of the illuminated tracks.\", \"Capture memorable photos and videos of your Luge experience.\", \"Participate in the night luge experience for enhanced visual effects and atmosphere.\", \"Explore the Imbiah Lookout area, where Skyline Luge is located.\", \"Enjoy the Jungle Trail Luge for a ride surrounded by lush greenery.\"]','2025-12-15 17:53:03','2025-12-15 17:53:03'),(92,235,'{\"email\": {\"url\": \"mailto:enquiry@snowcity.com.sg\", \"value\": \"enquiry@snowcity.com.sg\"}, \"phone\": {\"url\": \"tel:+6565602306\", \"value\": \"+65 6560 2306\"}, \"website\": {\"url\": \"http://www.snowcity.com.sg/\", \"value\": \"www.snowcity.com.sg\"}}','Snow City provides wheelchair access throughout the facility. Elevators are available to access different levels. Accessible restrooms are also available for visitors with disabilities.','Year-round (indoor attraction)','[{\"day\": \"Monday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Tuesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Wednesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Thursday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Friday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Saturday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Sunday\",