close_time\": \"17:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Tuesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"08:30\", \"close_time\": \"17:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Wednesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"08:30\", \"close_time\": \"17:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Thursday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"08:30\", \"close_time\": \"17:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Friday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"08:30\", \"close_time\": \"17:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Saturday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"08:30\", \"close_time\": \"17:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Sunday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"08:30\", \"close_time\": \"17:30\"}]','Asen\'s Fortress is a medieval fortress situated in the Rhodope Mountains near Asenovgrad, Bulgaria. Known for its strategic location and well-preserved church, it offers stunning panoramic views. Explore centuries of history and breathtaking scenery.',90,'[\"Explore the ruins of the medieval fortress walls and towers.\", \"Visit the well-preserved Church of the Holy Mother of God.\", \"Enjoy panoramic views of the Rhodope Mountains and surrounding area.\", \"Learn about the fortress\'s rich history dating back to the Roman era.\", \"Capture stunning photographs of the landscape.\", \"Hike along the scenic trails leading to and from the fortress.\", \"Discover the defensive architecture and strategic importance of the site.\", \"Imagine life in the medieval era within this historic stronghold.\"]','2025-12-15 17:53:39','2025-12-15 17:53:39'),(98,241,'{\"email\": {\"url\": null, \"value\": null}, \"phone\": {\"url\": \"tel:+35933272277\", \"value\": \"+359 33 272 277\"}, \"website\": {\"url\": \"http://www.bachkovskimanastir.com/\", \"value\": \"www.bachkovskimanastir.com\"}}','Bachkovo Monastery has limited accessibility. The main courtyard is relatively flat, but many areas, including some chapels and the ossuary, are accessed by stairs. There are no elevators or dedicated facilities for disabled visitors.','Spring (April-June) or Fall (September-Octobe