_W1Xo',4.60,25761,'The Bridge of Sighs enchants visitors with its beauty and rich history, connecting the past to Venice\'s romantic present. It offers a memorable and cinematic experience, especially when viewed from a gondola or from within, solidifying its place as a must-see landmark.',45.434050,12.340854,'30124 Venice, Metropolitan City of Venice, Italy','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 18:54:23'),(274,26,'ca-rezzonico-museum','Ca’ Rezzonico Museum','Ca\' Rezzonico','ChIJ10rFUc6xfkcRXf3NUR_5e78',4.50,3238,'Visitors adore Ca\' Rezzonico for its stunning architecture, rich history, and immersive glimpse into 18th-century Venetian life. The museum showcases beautiful art, lavishly decorated rooms, and period furnishings, offering a \"wow\" experience in a charming and often uncrowded setting. It\'s a must-see destination along the Grand Canal.',45.433541,12.326826,'Sestiere Dorsoduro, 3136, 30123 Venezia VE, Italy','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 18:55:56'),(275,26,'carlo-goldoni-s-house','Carlo Goldoni’s House','Carlo Goldoni\'s House','ChIJ9ddre8WxfkcRmt-FWhwMDEI',3.60,327,'Visitors appreciate this charming, small museum for its unique collection of marionettes and historical insights into Carlo Goldoni\'s life and work. The museum offers a glimpse into 18th-century Venetian theater and culture through costumes, furniture, and reconstructions of Goldoni\'s plays. It\'s a worthwhile stop, especially if you have a museum pass.',45.436192,12.328306,'Rio Terà dei Nomboli, 2794, 30125 Venezia VE, Italy','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 18:57:25'),(276,26,'catamaran-cruise','Catamaran Cruise','Venezia Catamaran Cruises','ChIJDxt-DHKvfkcR_JXrsQdLwO0',4.90,533,'Visitors rave about the relaxing atmosphere and stunning views of Venice offered by Venezia Catamaran Cruises. The friendly staff, delicious drinks, and live music create a memorable experience, especially during the sunset. It\'s a highly recommended way to unwind and see the city from a unique perspective.',45.431797,12.351050,'Opposite Restaurant La Nuova Perla, Via Giuseppe Garibaldi, 1645, 30122 Venezia VE, Italy','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 18:58:38'),(277,26,'concerts-in-vivaldi-church','Concerts in Vivaldi Church','Chiesa della Pietà - Santa Maria della Visitazione','ChIJZQOQOiaufkcR3G6Ed4uWAtU',4.70,1307,'Visitors rave about the beautiful church and the fantastic Vivaldi concerts held within. The music, often performed by talented musicians like the Interpreti Veneziani, is described as a must-see experience, particularly with Tiepolo\'s ceiling fresco as a backdrop.',45.434061,12.344937,'Riva degli Schiavoni, 30122 Venezia VE, Italy','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:00:24'),(278,26,'doge-s-palace','Doge’s Palace','Doge\'s Palace','ChIJiYRBbtexfkcR0XTK3ATSCbg',4.70,36469,'Visitors rave about the Doge\'s Palace as a breathtaking must-see, filled with history, incredible art, and ornate architecture. They recommend booking tickets in advance and setting aside at least two hours to fully explore the palace and learn about its rich history, with many suggesting a tour guide.',45.433704,12.340389,'P.za San Marco, 1, 30124 Venezia VE, Italy','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:01:33'),(279,26,'dolomites-tour','Dolomites Tour','Avventure Bellissime','ChIJAQAAwNCxfkcR-vJs_2DKAy8',4.30,60,'Visitors consistently praise Avventure Bellissime for their expertly planned and stress-free tours throughout Italy, highlighting knowledgeable guides and seamless logistics. They create unforgettable, personalized experiences, catering to individual needs and ensuring every detail is perfect.',45.481614,12.280153,'Via Barbana, 6, 30173 Venezia VE, Italy','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:03:20'),(280,26,'garden-of-villa-barbarigo-in-valsanzibio','Garden of Villa Barbarigo in Valsanzibio','Garden of Villa Barbarigo in Valsanzibio','ChIJcfboWHDgfkcRfaWlVOBwQ3Y',4.60,4063,'Visitors adore the Garden of Villa Barbarigo as a tranquil and enchanting escape, especially highlighting the meticulously maintained gardens and the thrilling hedge maze. The unique features like the island of rabbits and beautiful water features add to the magical experience, making it a hit with both adults and children.',45.291422,11.727406,'Via Diana, 2 35030, di Valsanzibio PD, Italy','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:04:55'),(281,26,'lace-museum','Lace Museum','Lace Museum','ChIJYbdxP1KsfkcRqiFOoX7hBWM',4.20,1905,'Visitors appreciate the Lace Museum\'s beautiful and intricate lacework, presented in a peaceful and informative setting. The museum offers a glimpse into the history of Venetian lace-making, especially for those already visiting Burano. It\'s often described as a worthwhile, if brief, stop.',45.484742,12.418762,'P.za Baldassarre Galuppi, 187, 30142 Venezia VE, Italy','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:06:52'),(282,26,'m9-museum-of-the-20th-century','M9 – Museum of the 20th Century','Museo M9 Mestre','ChIJBfbdmz-0fkcRT8E5XfLS2Pk',4.60,2920,'Visitors rave about Museo M9\'s modern and interactive exhibits that bring contemporary Italian history to life. The museum is praised for being informative, engaging, and accessible in both Italian and English, making it a must-visit destination for those in Venice.',45.491701,12.241046,'Via Giovanni Pascoli, 11, 30171 Venezia VE, Italy','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:08:47'),(283,26,'mask-workshop-in-venice','Mask Workshop in Venice','casanova mask artisan workshop','ChIJ075l-sSxfkcRWJiZd8w5-KI',4.90,73,'Visitors rave about Casanova Mask Artisan Workshop as an authentic experience where they can witness the mask-making process. They appreciate the artisan\'s knowledge, kindness, and high-quality, handmade masks, which include traditional Venetian designs. It\'s considered a hidden gem offering a less touristy, more personal experience.',45.438921,12.329598,'C. Seconda del Cristo, 2210, 30125 Venezia VE, Italy','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:10:18'),(284,26,'murano-glass-museum','Murano Glass Museum','Glass Museum (Murano)','ChIJk5aq4QOufkcRG_9yVn_-aQU',4.10,9246,'Visitors love the Glass Museum for its stunning collection of Murano glass art, showcasing the evolution of glassmaking from ancient times to modern designs. The museum offers a captivating journey through the history and artistry of Venetian glass, with highlights including elaborate centerpieces and a beautifully decorated main display room. Many found the size of the museum perfect to learn a lot without getting tired.',45.456564,12.356871,'Fondamenta Marco Giustinian, 8, 30141 Venezia VE, Italy','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:11:54'),(285,26,'palazzo-pisani','Palazzo Pisani','Palazzetto Pisani Grand Canal','ChIJVRFp6tGxfkcR2BHTlKmOiXE',4.40,558,'Visitors rave about Palazzetto Pisani\'s unique Venetian charm, describing it as a luxurious and authentic experience. The hotel\'s stunning historical atmosphere, coupled with excellent service and a convenient location on the Grand Canal, makes for an unforgettable stay.',45.432019,12.330318,'Fondamenta Narisi, 2814, 30124 Venezia VE, Italy','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:13:20'),(286,26,'photoshoot-in-venice','Photoshoot in Venice','Photographer Venice Pietro Volpato','ChIJsbw2l_i1fkcRjL0yVlxg5UU',5.00,221,'Visitors rave about Pietro\'s ability to make them feel comfortable while guiding them to beautiful, hidden locations in Venice. They appreciate his attention to detail, resulting in stunning and natural photos that capture special moments. Many also highlight his friendly personality and helpful recommendations, making the photoshoot a highlight of their trip.',45.441541,12.327893,'C. del Tentor, 1908, 30135 Venezia VE, Italy','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:14:32'),(287,26,'royal-palace-of-venice','Royal Palace of Venice','Doge\'s Palace','ChIJiYRBbtexfkcR0XTK3ATSCbg',4.70,36469,'Visitors adore the Doge\'s Palace for its breathtaking beauty, rich history, and stunning artwork. Many recommend booking tickets in advance to avoid lines and suggest allowing at least two hours to fully explore this must-see Venetian landmark.',45.433704,12.340389,'P.za San Marco, 1, 30124 Venezia VE, Italy','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:16:11'),(288,26,'teatro-la-fenice','Teatro La Fenice','Teatro La Fenice','ChIJr24y6dCxfkcRGiZJP4wZoig',4.70,15081,'Visitors adore Teatro La Fenice for its stunning beauty, rich history, and phoenix-like resilience. The opulent interiors, excellent acoustics, and sense of cultural significance create a breathtaking and immersive experience. Even without a performance, the tour is worthwhile, offering a glimpse into Venice\'s cultural past.',45.433638,12.333758,'Campo S. Fantin, 1965, 30124 Venezia VE, Italy','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:17:40'),(289,26,'vatican-chapels','Vatican Chapels','Vatican Chapels','ChIJB7Oy46OvfkcREFloCgsR9Q8',3.80,56,'Visitors appreciate the Vatican Chapels as a beautiful and serene escape from the Venetian crowds. The unique chapels, designed by international architects, offer a quiet space for reflection within a lovely garden setting. Booking a guided tour is now required to access this spiritual retreat.',45.427333,12.344172,'San Giorgio Maggiore, 30133 Venezia VE, Italy','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:19:13'),(290,26,'venice-boat-tour','Venice Boat Tour','Venice Tour by Boat','ChIJNasfj2ixfkcR5OIxOxLuufM',4.90,51,'Visitors rave about the personalized and beautiful boat tours led by Rachele and Marco. They highlight the hosts\' knowledge, attentiveness, and ability to showcase stunning and unique locations around Venice, often including special touches like wine and photography. Many consider it a must-do experience for an unforgettable visit.',45.443471,12.339878,'Ponte Donà, 30121 Venezia VE, Italy','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:21:03'),(291,26,'venice-clock-tower','Venice Clock Tower','Clock Tower','ChIJLbrmd9exfkcR4YVP0azgB4g',4.70,1890,'Visitors are impressed by the Clock Tower\'s beauty, iconic presence, and historical significance in Piazza San Marco. The clock\'s intricate mechanisms and rooftop views are highlights, although tours are required and should be booked in advance. The tower\'s bells are also a memorable part of the experience.',45.434759,12.338967,'P.za San Marco, 30124 Venezia VE, Italy','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:22:29'),(292,26,'venice-kayak-tour','Venice Kayak Tour','Venice Kayak','ChIJNXmIJVqufkcRbdoBTdBm8Os',4.90,104,'Visitors rave about Venice Kayak as a unique and unforgettable way to experience the city from the canals. The guided tours, particularly those with guides like Shamir, are highly praised for their knowledge, personalized experiences, and ability to showcase hidden gems of Venice.',45.443865,12.330366,'Calle Tornielli, 2370, 30121 Venezia VE, Italy','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:24:14'),(293,26,'venice-walking-tour','Venice Walking Tour','Venice Walking Tour','ChIJ-VKmdMGxfkcRmy-KP-i31vc',4.90,2254,'Visitors rave about the knowledgeable and engaging guides, like Riccardo, Maria Laura, Alice, and Mary, who share fascinating historical insights and local knowledge. They appreciate exploring both popular and less crowded areas of Venice while enjoying a well-organized and informative experience, often enhanced by listening devices. The tours are praised for their perfect blend of education and entertainment.',45.436056,12.335879,'Per S. Marco, 4765, 30124 Venezia VE, Italy','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:26:14'),(294,27,'albertina-museum','Albertina Museum','Albertina','ChIJwVp-8psHbUcRuN43n5iK72Y',4.70,33316,'Visitors love the Albertina for its diverse collection featuring masters like Picasso, Monet, and Van Gogh, along with well-organized and captivating exhibitions like the popular Modern Gothic display. Many also appreciate the stunning, free views from the terrace, especially at sunset.',48.204699,16.368182,'Albertinapl. 1, 1010 Wien, Austria','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:27:33'),(295,27,'austrian-dinner-show','Austrian Dinner Show','Austrian Dinner Show','ChIJU3Z98nkHbUcRF54Uz6RRZr0',4.10,72,'Visitors appreciate the talented musicians, singers, and dancers who provide an entertaining glimpse into Austrian culture. Many find the show enjoyable, especially considering its budget-friendly price compared to other similar events. However, the food quality receives mixed reviews and might not be the main highlight.',48.211144,16.358186,'Rathauspl. 1, 1010 Wien, Austria','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:29:17'),(296,27,'belvedere-palace','Belvedere Palace','Belvedere Palace','ChIJpZ4LAn0HbUcRB3aToFL8ZUo',4.70,83301,'Visitors rave about the Belvedere Palace\'s stunning art collections, especially works by famous painters like Klimt, within the beautiful baroque architecture. Many also enjoyed the charming Christmas markets held on the grounds and the lovely gardens, despite seasonal limitations. It\'s considered a must-see cultural experience in Vienna.',48.191475,16.380932,'1030 Vienna, Austria','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:30:24'),(297,27,'capuchins-crypt-vienna','Capuchins Crypt Vienna','Imperial Crypt','ChIJG0kLqp4HbUcRvbtOLMhP3gc',4.60,12091,'Visitors are captivated by the Imperial Crypt\'s rich history and the impressive artistry of the sarcophagi. The experience is described as both fascinating and awe-inspiring, offering a unique glimpse into the final resting place of Austrian royalty. Many feel the price is worth it to see such an important and historical location.',48.205715,16.370025,'Tegetthoffstraße 2, 1010 Wien, Austria','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:31:47'),(298,27,'danube-tower','Danube Tower','Danube Tower','ChIJO4ukqfYGbUcRS1HnY7K60Cw',4.60,19201,'Visitors rave about the Danube Tower\'s breathtaking panoramic views of Vienna and the Danube River. Many enjoy the unique experiences like the thrilling slide and the rotating restaurants, where they can savor delicious food and coffee while taking in the stunning cityscape. It\'s a highly recommended destination for an unforgettable experience.',48.240340,16.410051,'Donauturmplatz 1, 1220 Wien, Austria','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:33:23'),(299,27,'familypark','Familypark','Family Fun','ChIJl9xuSFMBbUcR3_FctrAUdIM',3.80,4400,'Visitors rave about Family Fun as a paradise for kids, highlighting the variety of engaging activities and the well-organized, clean environment. It\'s a popular spot for birthday parties and burning off energy, with parents appreciating the on-site restaurant and friendly staff.',48.252626,16.462384,'Breitenleer Str. 77, 1220 Wien, Austria','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:34:48'),(300,27,'ghosts-and-legends-tour','Ghosts and Legends Tour','Prague Ghosts Legends Museum','ChIJ99ji2uOUC0cRdh-KgDbeo8o',3.40,416,'Visitors appreciate the museum\'s spooky atmosphere and captivating storytelling, which bring Prague\'s haunted past to life. Some also enjoyed the interactive elements and the stories presented, especially with the audio guide. A humorous and engaging ticket seller made one visitor\'s experience particularly memorable.',50.087577,14.405866,'Mostecká 46/18, Malá Strana, 118 00 Praha-Praha 1, Czechia','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:36:28'),(301,27,'giant-ferris-wheel','Giant Ferris Wheel','Viennese Giant Ferris Wheel','ChIJJYWNjA8HbUcRBlfleWeh1qw',4.50,46643,'Visitors love the Viennese Giant Ferris Wheel for its breathtaking views of Vienna and the overall enjoyable experience. Many recommend booking tickets online for faster access, though the wait is manageable, and highlight the comfortable cabins. It\'s considered a special and memorable attraction, especially around sunset or during festive times.',48.216700,16.395901,'Gaudeegasse 1, 1020 Wien, Austria','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:38:01'),(302,27,'haus-der-musik','Haus der Musik','House of Music','ChIJVVf9x50HbUcRPYtBoZmur0g',4.50,10706,'Visitors love the House of Music for its engaging and interactive exhibits that make learning about music fun for all ages. Many also appreciate the intimate and affordable concerts, especially those featuring string ensembles. It\'s a highly recommended experience for families and music lovers alike.',48.203874,16.373046,'Seilerstätte 30, 1010 Wien, Austria','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:39:20'),(303,27,'imperial-treasury','Imperial Treasury','Imperial Treasury','ChIJ3wYgv5kHbUcRf_qQCrZSEa8',4.60,8239,'Visitors rave about the Imperial Treasury\'s impressive collection of jewels, crowns, and historical treasures, finding the sheer size and beauty of the gems mind-blowing. Many recommend the audio guide for a more engaging experience and to truly appreciate the grandeur of the Austrian Empire.',48.206739,16.365773,'Schweizerhof, Hofburg, 1010 Wien, Austria','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:40:29'),(304,28,'amaze-amsterdam','Amaze Amsterdam','AMAZE Amsterdam','ChIJ2xlnX77jxUcR2WgrWg7Ehxk',4.50,7164,'Visitors rave about AMAZE Amsterdam\'s immersive and unique experience, highlighting the cool rooms with lights, sounds, and lasers. The friendly and helpful staff also receive consistent praise. It\'s a highly recommended activity for those who appreciate art, electronic music, and interactive visuals.',52.393835,4.851689,'Elementenstraat 25, 1014 AR Amsterdam, Netherlands','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:42:16'),(305,28,'amsterdam-canal-cruise','Amsterdam Canal Cruise','Amsterdam Canal Cruises','ChIJIaP3F-0JxkcRsjmw80fNMrA',4.40,2191,'Amsterdam canal cruises are a must-do for first-time visitors, offering a relaxing and scenic way to see the city\'s iconic canals, bridges, and historic architecture. Many appreciate the informative commentary, comfortable boats (even in winter), and the unique perspective of Amsterdam from the water. It\'s an excellent way to get an overview of the city and its attractions.',52.358171,4.891628,'Stadhouderskade 550, 1072 AE Amsterdam, Netherlands','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:43:54'),(306,28,'amsterdam-dungeon','Amsterdam Dungeon','Dungeon Amsterdam','ChIJC7Uw48AJxkcR28umcgx0C6k',4.50,13682,'Visitors rave about the Dungeon Amsterdam\'s immersive and engaging experience, highlighting the brilliant actors and their passionate performances. The combination of scary, funny, and surprising moments, along with interactive storytelling, makes it a highly recommended and memorable attraction.',52.370160,4.892111,'The Amsterdam Dungeon, Rokin 78, 1012 KW Amsterdam, Netherlands','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:45:35'),(307,28,'amsterdam-royal-palace','Amsterdam Royal Palace','Royal Palace Amsterdam','ChIJFQ6IwMYJxkcRis8dtZlOkTk',4.60,25768,'Visitors rave about the Royal Palace\'s stunning interior, rich history, and magnificent architecture. The audio tour is a highlight, offering flexible and informative exploration of the palace\'s beautiful rooms and world-class art. It\'s a gem that\'s well worth the time to discover a fascinating part of Dutch history.',52.373184,4.891376,'Nieuwezijds Voorburgwal 147, 1012 RJ Amsterdam, Netherlands','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:47:13'),(308,28,'amsterdam-zoo','Amsterdam Zoo','ARTIS','ChIJYQCs26EJxkcRPUqKm3hTaA4',4.50,35384,'Visitors adore ARTIS for its beautiful setting, well-cared for animals, and engaging exhibits like the planetarium and aquarium. The zoo offers a memorable experience for all ages, with plenty to see and explore in a peaceful atmosphere.',52.366000,4.916532,'Plantage Kerklaan 38-40, 1018 CZ Amsterdam, Netherlands','2025-12-15 12:22:23','2025-12-15 19:48:57');
