INSERT INTO `audience_profiles` VALUES (18,232,'families_with_young_children','The Singapore Zoo is an excellent destination for families with young children. The open concept provides safe viewing of animals. Kid-friendly exhibits such as the Rainforest Kidzworld offer interactive learning and play areas. Families can enjoy the animal shows and feeding sessions, creating memorable experiences. The zoo\'s focus on conservation also provides an opportunity to educate children about wildlife and environmental responsibility. Stroller rentals and family-friendly dining options are readily available.','👨‍👩‍👧‍👦','2025-12-15 17:54:27'),(19,232,'nature_lovers','The Singapore Zoo, with its \'open zoo\' concept, provides an immersive experience for nature lovers. Lush landscaping and naturalistic habitats allow visitors to observe animals in environments that mimic their native homes. The zoo\'s focus on biodiversity and conservation efforts appeals to those interested in wildlife preservation. Birdwatching opportunities abound, and the peaceful atmosphere offers a relaxing escape from the city. Visitors can learn about various ecosystems and the importance of protecting endangered species.','🌿','2025-12-15 17:54:27'),(20,232,'photographers','The Singapore Zoo presents a fantastic opportunity for photographers of all skill levels. The open concept and naturalistic enclosures allow for capturing stunning images of animals in settings that mimic their wild habitats. The zoo\'s diverse collection of animals provides a wide range of photographic subjects, from majestic big cats to colorful birds. Golden hour provides exceptional lighting and unique photo opportunities. With careful planning and patience, photographers can create a portfolio of remarkable wildlife images.','📸','2025-12-15 17:54:27'),(21,232,'international_tourists','As a world-renowned attraction, the Singapore Zoo is a must-visit for international tourists. Its unique \'open zoo\' concept offers an unparalleled wildlife experience. The zoo\'s diverse collection of animals from around the globe showcases biodiversity. English signage and readily available information make navigating the zoo easy. It offers a glimpse into Singapore\'s commitment to conservation and eco-tourism. The zoo is easily accessible and conveniently located near other attractions, making it a great addition to any Singapore itinerary.','🌍','2025-12-15 17:54:27'),(22,233,'families','Great for families with children of all ages seeking a memorable experience. The panoramic views of Singapore offer a fantastic educational opportunity, allowing children to learn about the city\'s geography and landmarks. The observation deck provides a safe and accessible environment for families to enjoy stunning views together. Perfect for creating lasting memories with photo opportunities and shared moments of wonder.','👨‍👩‍👧‍👦','2025-12-15 17:56:19'),(23,233,'couples','Romantic spot perfect for date nights and special occasions. The breathtaking sunset views over the city skyline provide a stunning backdrop for romantic moments. The observation deck offers a sophisticated ambiance and a chance to create unforgettable memories. Enjoy a leisurely stroll, share intimate conversations, and capture beautiful photos together. A perfect place to celebrate love and create lasting memories.','💑','2025-12-15 17:56:19'),(24,233,'solo_travelers','Ideal for solo exploration and reflection while taking in unparalleled views of Singapore. The observation deck provides a space for quiet contemplation and appreciation of the city\'s beauty. A perfect opportunity to connect with the city on a personal level, capturing stunning photos and creating lasting memories. The experience allows for a sense of independence and self-discovery amidst the urban landscape.','🚶','2025-12-15 17:56:19'),(25,233,'photographers','A haven for photographers seeking stunning cityscapes and architectural marvels. The Skypark Observation Deck offers unparalleled panoramic views of Singapore, providing a multitude of photographic opportunities. Capture breathtaking sunsets, shimmering city lights, and iconic landmarks from a unique vantage point. Experiment with different angles, compositions, and lighting conditions to create stunning images.','📸','2025-12-15 17:56:19'),(26,233,'architecture_fans','An architectural enthusiast\'s dream, offering unparalleled views of Singapore\'s skyline and the Marina Bay Sands itself. Appreciate the intricate details of the surrounding buildings and the innovative design of the Skypark. The observation deck provides a unique perspective on the urban landscape, showcasing the city\'s architectural evolution. Marvel at the harmonious blend of modern and traditional designs.','🏛️','2025-12-15 17:56:19'),(27,234,'families','Families with children of all ages will find Skyline Luge Sentosa to be an exciting and memorable experience. The Luge offers a unique, part go-kart, part toboggan ride that\'s easy to control, making it accessible even for young children. The Skyride provides stunning views of Sentosa and the surrounding waters. It\'s a great way to create lasting family memories with a mix of thrill and scenic beauty. Multiple rides are often purchased, providing hours of fun for everyone.','👨‍👩‍👧‍👦','2025-12-15 17:58:23'),(28,234,'adventure_seekers','Thrill-seekers will appreciate the customizable nature of the Luge experience. Each ride can be different depending on how fast you choose to go and the lines you take on the track. The four different Luge tracks offer varying levels of challenge and excitement, ensuring there\'s something for every level of adventure enthusiast. The combination of speed, control, and the stunning scenery makes for an adrenaline-pumping activity. Night Luge sessions add another layer of thrill with vibrant lighting effects.','🏔️','2025-12-15 17:58:23'),(29,234,'couples','Couples looking for a fun and unique date experience will enjoy Skyline Luge Sentosa. The shared thrill of the Luge ride creates a memorable bonding experience. The Skyride offers a romantic setting with panoramic views, especially beautiful during sunset. Night Luge provides a vibrant and exciting atmosphere for a date night. Photos and videos can be taken to capture the special moments. Overall, a unique and exciting experience to share.','💑','2025-12-15 17:58:23'),(30,234,'tourist_groups','Skyline Luge is an ideal activity for tour groups visiting Sentosa. It offers a fun and interactive experience that caters to a wide range of ages and abilities. The attraction can accommodate large groups, and the multiple Luge tracks ensure there\'s something for everyone. It\'s a great way to break up sightseeing with an engaging and exciting activity. The souvenir shop offers a chance to purchase mementos of the experience.','🧑‍🤝‍🧑','2025-12-15 17:58:23'),(31,235,'families_with_young_children','Snow City is a fantastic destination for families with young children, especially those who haven\'t experienced snow before. Kids can build snowmen, play in the snow playground, and enjoy gentle slides. The indoor setting provides a safe and controlled environment for little ones to explore the winter wonderland. Parents can relax and watch their children\'s delight as they discover the magic of snow in a tropical country. Warm clothing rental makes it hassle-free for families to enjoy the experience. There are also designated areas for younger children, ensuring their safety and enjoyment.','👨‍👩‍👧‍👦','2025-12-15 18:00:56'),(32,235,'adventure_seekers','Adventure seekers looking for a unique experience in Singapore will find Snow City appealing. While not an extreme sport, the Snow City offers opportunities for thrilling activities like snow tubing down a 60-meter long slope. The sub-zero temperatures and icy environment provide a change from the tropical climate, offering a refreshing challenge. Participants can test their balance and coordination on the slippery surfaces. Occasional themed events and activities, such as ice sculpting workshops or snow zorbing, add to the adventurous appeal.','🏔️','2025-12-15 18:00:56'),(33,235,'couples_seeking_novelty','Couples looking for a fun and unusual date idea in Singapore can escape the heat at Snow City. The novelty of experiencing snow in a tropical country creates a memorable and unique experience. Couples can enjoy playful activities together, such as building a snowman or having a friendly snowball fight. The romantic ambiance of the snowy setting provides a backdrop for intimate moments. The attraction also offers opportunities for taking memorable photos together in winter-themed settings.','💑','2025-12-15 18:00:56'),(34,235,'students_and_youth_groups','Snow City is a popular destination for school excursions and youth group outings. It provides an engaging and educational experience about winter environments, which is a stark contrast to Singapore\'s tropical climate. Students can learn about the properties of snow and ice through interactive displays and activities. The attraction promotes teamwork and collaboration through snow-related games and challenges. It also provides a fun and social environment for students to bond and create lasting memories.','🎓','2025-12-15 18:00:56'),(35,236,'families_with_young_children','SuperPark Singapore is a fantastic destination for families with young children. The designated kids\' area offers a safe and engaging environment for toddlers and preschoolers to explore and play. Activities like the soft play area, pedal car track, and mini obstacle courses provide age-appropriate challenges and endless fun. Parents can relax knowing their little ones are entertained and safe in a stimulating environment designed for their developmental needs. Expect a day filled with laughter, active play, and creating lasting memories as a family.','👶','2025-12-15 18:03:00'),(36,236,'teenagers_and_young_adults','SuperPark Singapore is a thrilling haven for teenagers and young adults seeking adrenaline-pumping activities and social interaction. The Adventure Area offers challenging obstacles, trampoline platforms, and climbing walls, perfect for testing their physical limits and pushing their boundaries. The Game Arena provides opportunities for friendly competition with activities like street basketball, super soccer, and super bowling. Socialize with friends, unleash your inner athlete, and experience a day of exhilarating fun and friendly rivalry. Expect to break a sweat, laugh a lot, and create unforgettable memories with your friends.','🤸','2025-12-15 18:03:00'),(37,236,'corporate_teams','SuperPark Singapore offers a unique and engaging team-building experience for corporate teams. The diverse range of activities promotes collaboration, communication, and problem-solving skills in a fun and informal setting. Teams can bond over friendly competitions in the Game Arena, challenge themselves in the Adventure Area, or simply enjoy a lighthearted day of physical activity. The park provides a refreshing break from the office environment, fostering stronger relationships and boosting team morale. Expect a day of laughter, camaraderie, and a renewed sense of teamwork.','🧑‍💼','2025-12-15 18:03:00'),(38,236,'adventure_seekers','SuperPark Singapore caters to adrenaline junkies and adventure enthusiasts with its thrilling range of activities. The Adventure Area challenges individuals to push their physical limits with climbing walls, ziplines, and obstacle courses. The trampoline platform allows for high-flying acrobatics and gravity-defying stunts. The park offers a safe and controlled environment to experience the thrill of adventure and test your courage. Expect a day of adrenaline-pumping fun, pushing your boundaries, and conquering new challenges.','🧗','2025-12-15 18:03:00'),(39,237,'families_with_young_children','Universal Studios Singapore offers a magical experience for families with young children. Themed areas like