 outdoor sides, and wear comfortable shoes because there are many large pieces around.','2025-10-28 15:15:22','Google','2025-12-15 18:21:10'),(102,248,'Thomas Winslett','https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101218693711856183355/reviews','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWCFTTe0E2--7pRHceSn4hb1-36RBn5hf0mQZXUXKwYenhndvY8rg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6',5,'This was so much more than what I could have imagined. The extent and quality of the museum was incredible. The staff were kind and helpful.\nAs you enter the grounds you see a large quality of vehicles, aircraft and other equipment, mostly from WWII and the cold war era.\nThe museum itself is a multi-level building that is laid out very well. There is a center staircase and as you ascend you enter a different time period. Each of the wings has a different theme (clothing, medals/awards, equipment, etc).','2025-06-30 12:49:36','Google','2025-12-15 18:21:10'),(103,248,'Pamela','https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106882663617521474017/reviews','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXV9C3JZCfAj3LazPQLYRg3uYkWvqf7ZxiqI_riOaifcR_5vcBU=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5',4,'Very interesting and informative. There are different ticket packages depending on how much you want to see.\nThe entrance exhibition is free, but you can also buy a ticket for the 2nd outdoor exhibition or choose a package to access the other floors.\nWorth exploring if you have time.','2025-08-27 20:53:28','Google','2025-12-15 18:21:10'),(104,248,'Vito Habjanič','https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111338702538221719321/reviews','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWcr099TF3GeAO0U2khqsFYJtZR0iGK2Aqk8KWKEGibIuhaMJU6=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4',5,'Visited on a Sunday morning, no queue, no wait; you just enter. Great museum, a lot to see: a lot of tanks, armored vehicles, and aviation-related stuff. The museum building is superb and leads you through all of the history of Bulgaria.','2025-07-13 20:18:54','Google','2025-12-15 18:21:10'),(105,248,'Sean Zammit','https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109238056289402953409/reviews','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKPbeLwja9uYwfxvMaWEzo1c73wpR9Lq0nseDoNzLXGV4yySg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo',5,'Massive collection of good condition ww2, soviet and modern military vehicles, tanks and aircraft for free on display and a well kept diverse collection of military equipment, uniforms and pieces in the paid museum section. Definitely one of the best military museums','2025-08-16 07:22:02','Google','2025-12-15 18:21:10'),(106,249,'Elena *','https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106763654610327838943/reviews','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWgJM-bv7QDhKW9Cy87YWrc65BlF1aPR7KUWdJ7SOxb6Bty-H2p=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5',5,'Amazing experience to connect with wild nature, explore Bulgarian nature beauty and get an amazing experience in check your own abilities in climbing, walking and etc. All the way you can admire picturesque panoramic view, wild flowers, birds and if you’re lucky -wild animals) We visited Pirin in the middle of July and at midday it was hot that’s why we waked up early to come back to parking near Vihren hut until midday\n\nMore about trips on born_to_lovve','2025-07-27 13:18:41','Google','2025-12-15 18:22:33'),(107,249,'shim shim','https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109861365405707586068/reviews','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLm3s_997SNMaLpTeixnhWKxoiRWcM5nIpsW-UoaEnc3IJygA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6',4,'Wonderful nature , great place for hiking though not the best route designation\nWent there when there was some snow and didn’t see all the route markings.','2025-10-15 06:58:10','Google','2025-12-15 18:22:33'),(108,249,'Peter Johannesen','https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100918434218570711830/reviews','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrIghOL9RGDrklCGySafN-v74Y5sTxij4w71HkgVrj8QZ0qf6I=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3',5,'Much to see. So far only four lakes, but definitely exploring this more. Good trails between and easy to see','2025-06-26 19:24:21','Google','2025-12-15 18:22:33'),(109,249,'George Papadopoulos','https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109682511574370087337/reviews','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDBbeKK2Rgi7Cg5MuA3RWm4hchX5eELr8DB8PkH7Ke_GV8n4Bs=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6',5,'Liked the slopes and facilities, even though everything closes a little early.  Beautiful nature, Ski passes are reasonably priced.  Can get a bit too busy on some days, but overall a great experience.  Keep in mind that driving might not be your best option on a busy day.','2018-03-13 13:01:14','Google','2025-12-15 18:22:33'),(110,249,'Alex Hoare','https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117200374529954925368/reviews','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8YiUfcDaBDr25cEmsW2oyP6KdGasDsw8p1oPsehUXK4CsEwye=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4',5,'Pirin National Park is an absolutely stunning place to hike and be immersed in nature.\n\nThe trails in the alpine are clearly marked and well maintained and the huts around the park are wonderful to stay in.\n\nThere are many trails to choose from and peaks to climb.\n\nBeautiful lakes, crystal clear streams, stunning mountains and breathtaking views Pirin is genuinely one of the most beautiful places I have ever been.\n\nPerfect if you want to visit just for one day or spend several nights in the park.','2023-10-06 11:14:47','Google','2025-12-15 18:22:33'),(111,250,'Jelena Klaric','https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103208663306484176105/reviews','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIbFeUPz1TqFif92ENb51-CDeCwIh56DW0wmhvV-fB3Th9Vqw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2',5,'Amazing day trip from Sofia to Plovdiv!\n\nWe had a fantastic day tour from Sofia to Plovdiv and couldn’t have asked for better guides. Maria and Sonya were absolutely wonderful — friendly, professional, and full of interesting stories about the history and culture of Plovdiv.\n\nThey made everything easy and enjoyable, from the travel to the sightse