itement, and unforgettable memories.','2025-10-16 13:37:20','Google','2025-12-15 19:33:23'),(352,298,'Achref Rihani','https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109978639890384077593/reviews','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKK7Z8hhG3mSZFWgR7Fa5sy2wCZ1qYnbavH6UQS4r4GDJLezQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2',5,'Highly recommended.\nDon\'t forget to try the slide, only for 6 euros, so unique experience and you don\'t need any reservation in the restaurant for it.\nNote: don\'t forget to reserve your place at the restaurant 3 days before if u wanna have coffee at 170 m hight.','2025-12-07 22:31:22','Google','2025-12-15 19:33:23'),(353,298,'Alexandra Anastasiu','https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/118393977225178724511/reviews','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW_zbMY7OgvC3TwVt4ii6rLVE_hBXTqwrt38GHvfNckBncnMZ1rmw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4',5,'Super cool 360° view of the city daytime but especially at  night. Lovely revolving Café at the top, that allows you to enjoy a pretty decent and afordable coffee and strudel while amazing views of the city are unfolding in front of you. Highly recommend the experience!!','2025-10-11 10:00:27','Google','2025-12-15 19:33:23'),(354,298,'Andjela Suskavcevic','https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104528416457128681252/reviews','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLYA9x2Lm4Sdlfxkp2ykDp2k8Dtf6alYXfQ6CaCehKuSgVbDQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4',5,'A great experience! The view from the top is amazing — you can see all of Vienna and the Danube River. The tower is clean and well organized, and the café with the rotating floor is a lovely touch. I highly recommend visiting!','2025-10-23 20:51:32','Google','2025-12-15 19:33:23'),(355,298,'Rajala Mahesh','https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/118074346984609383954/reviews','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjViZio5MqOFdZraEfggD6BTZmuCE-WToZ5j68FhJBv3-2VFXw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6',5,'My genuine opinion after visiting this on 09-10-2025. We have bought a tickets of 