INSERT INTO `tips` VALUES (79,232,'SAFETY','Watch out for the weather! Bring an umbrella or poncho; you\'ll likely encounter rain during your visit, which can make pathways slippery.','Reddit (Singapore Zoo)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:54:19'),(80,232,'SAFETY','Stay hydrated throughout the day. Singapore\'s humidity can be intense, especially when walking around the zoo. Bring a refillable water bottle and use the water fountains to stay cool and avoid heatstroke.','Reddit (Singapore Zoo)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:54:19'),(81,232,'SAFETY','Be aware of your surroundings near animal enclosures. While the zoo prioritizes safety, always maintain a respectful distance and follow posted guidelines to avoid any unexpected interactions.','Reddit (Singapore Zoo)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:54:19'),(82,232,'SAFETY','Apply sunscreen liberally and reapply throughout the day. Even on cloudy days, the sun\'s rays can be strong in Singapore, and you\'ll be spending a lot of time outdoors.','Reddit (Singapore Zoo)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:54:19'),(83,232,'SAFETY','Keep an eye on your belongings, especially in crowded areas like show venues and dining areas. While Singapore is generally safe, petty theft can occur.','Reddit (Singapore Zoo)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:54:19'),(84,232,'SAFETY','Wear comfortable, closed-toe shoes. You\'ll be doing a lot of walking, and the terrain can be uneven in some areas.','Reddit (Singapore Zoo)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:54:19'),(85,232,'INSIDER','Prioritize Singapore Zoo if you\'re short on time; it has more animals than Rainforest Wild.','Reddit (Singapore Zoo)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:54:19'),(86,232,'INSIDER','Combine Singapore Zoo with the Night Safari for a full day of animal encounters.','Reddit (Singapore Zoo)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:54:19'),(87,232,'INSIDER','Consider purchasing an express pass to Singapore Zoo if queues are a concern. This allows you to maximize your time and see more animals, especially during peak season.','Reddit (Singapore Zoo)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:54:19'),(88,232,'INSIDER','Check the show schedule in advance and plan your day around the animal shows you want to see. Arrive early to secure a good seat, as they can get crowded.','Reddit (Singapore Zoo)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:54:19'),(89,232,'INSIDER','Take advantage of the tram service to cover larger distances within the zoo, especially if you have limited time or mobility issues. It\'s a great way to see the park quickly.','Reddit (Singapore Zoo)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:54:19'),(90,232,'INSIDER','Pack snacks and drinks to avoid overspending on food and beverages inside the zoo. However, be mindful of the zoo\'s regulations regarding outside food.','Reddit (Singapore Zoo)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:54:19'),(91,232,'INSIDER','If you\'re interested in a unique experience, consider the \'Wild Cavern Adventure\' at Rainforest Wild, but be aware that Singapore Zoo has a greater variety of animals overall.','Reddit (Singapore Zoo)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:54:19'),(92,233,'SAFETY','Be mindful of the height; stay behind designated barriers, especially if you\'re prone to vertigo or traveling with small children.','Reddit (Skypark Observation Deck)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:56:12'),(93,233,'SAFETY','Watch your belongings closely at the Skypark Observation Deck. Due to the popularity and crowds, it\'s essential to keep an eye on your valuables to prevent theft or accidental loss.','Reddit (Skypark Observation Deck)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:56:12'),(94,233,'SAFETY','Check weather conditions before heading up to the Skypark Observation Deck. High winds or thunderstorms may lead to temporary closures or limit visibility from the top.','Reddit (Skypark Observation Deck)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:56:12'),(95,233,'SAFETY','Wear appropriate footwear. The Skypark Observation Deck is a large area, and you might be doing a fair amount of walking. Comfortable shoes are recommended to avoid discomfort.','Reddit (Skypark Observation Deck)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:56:12'),(96,233,'SAFETY','Stay hydrated, especially during hot days. Bring a bottle of water with you when visiting the Skypark Observation Deck, as it can get quite warm, and water may be expensive to purchase on-site.','Reddit (Skypark Observation Deck)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:56:12'),(97,233,'SAFETY','Be aware of your surroundings and other visitors, especially during peak hours at the Skypark Observation Deck. Avoid obstructing views for others and maintain a safe distance from the edge.','Reddit (Skypark Observation Deck)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:56:12'),(98,233,'INSIDER','Go early or late to avoid peak crowds at the Skypark Observation Deck for a more enjoyable experience.','Reddit (Skypark Observation Deck)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:56:12'),(99,233,'INSIDER','Look for bundled tickets that include the Skypark Observation Deck and other Marina Bay Sands attractions for potential cost savings.','Reddit (Skypark Observation Deck)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:56:12'),(100,233,'INSIDER','Time your visit to coincide with the Marina Bay Sands light show for a spectacular view from above. Check the show schedule in advance to plan accordingly.','Reddit (Skypark Observation Deck)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:56:12'),(101,233,'INSIDER','Consider visiting during the shoulder seasons (e.g., March-May, September-November) for pleasant weather and fewer tourists at the Skypark Observation Deck.','Reddit (Skypark Observation Deck)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:56:12'),(102,233,'INSIDER','Check for online discounts or promotions on tickets to the Skypark Observation Deck before your visit. Several websites and apps may offer discounted rates or special deals.','Reddit (Skypark Observation Deck)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:56:12'),(103,233,'INSIDER','Take advantage of the Skypark Observation Deck’s photo opportunities, especially during sunset for stunning panoramic views of Singapore\'s skyline, but be patient due to crowds.','Reddit (Skypark Observation Deck)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:56:12'),(104,233,'INSIDER','If you\'re not staying at Marina Bay Sands, the Skypark Observation Deck offers one of the best vantage points for seeing the Supertree Grove at Gardens by the Bay from a distance.','Reddit (Skypark Observation Deck)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:56:12'),(105,234,'SAFETY','Always follow the instructions given by the Luge staff carefully, especially regarding braking and steering. A momentary lapse in concentration could lead to an accident.','Reddit (Skyline Luge Sentosa)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:58:15'),(106,234,'SAFETY','Ensure that your helmet fits properly and is securely fastened before starting your Luge ride. A loose helmet offers minimal protection in case of a collision.','Reddit (Skyline Luge Sentosa)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:58:15'),(107,234,'SAFETY','Maintain a safe distance from the Luge in front of you, especially on steeper sections of the track. Sudden stops by other riders could cause a rear-end collision.','Reddit (Skyline Luge Sentosa)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:58:15'),(108,234,'SAFETY','Be extra cautious when riding the Luge at night, as visibility may be reduced. Pay close attention to the track ahead and adjust your speed accordingly.','Reddit (Skyline Luge Sentosa)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:58:15'),(109,234,'SAFETY','If you\'re riding with children, make sure they are tall enough and capable of controlling the Luge safely. Consider riding tandem with younger children who might struggle with steering or braking.','Reddit (Skyline Luge Sentosa)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:58:15'),(110,234,'SAFETY','Avoid bringing loose items like phones or cameras on the Luge ride that could fall out and distract you or other riders. Use a secure phone holder or ask someone to take photos from the side.','Reddit (Skyline Luge Sentosa)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:58:15'),(111,234,'INSIDER','Go early or late to avoid long queues, especially during peak season and weekends.','Reddit (Skyline Luge Sentosa)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:58:15'),(112,234,'INSIDER','Purchase multiple rides to save money; the more you ride, the cheaper it gets per ride.','Reddit (Skyline Luge Sentosa)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:58:15'),(113,234,'INSIDER','Consider the timing of your visit to coincide with the sunset for a beautiful view from the Skyride. The lighting makes for amazing photos and a memorable experience.','Reddit (Skyline Luge Sentosa)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:58:15'),(114,234,'INSIDER','If it\'s your first time, take the time to familiarize yourself with the Luge controls at the practice track before heading up the Skyride. This will make your ride much more enjoyable and safer.','Reddit (Skyline Luge Sentosa)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:58:15'),(115,234,'INSIDER','Check for online deals or combination packages that include the Skyline Luge with other Sentosa attractions. This can help you save money and make the most of your visit.','Reddit (Skyline Luge Sentosa)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:58:15'),(116,234,'INSIDER','Opt for the night Luge experience for a unique and thrilling adventure. The track is lit up with colorful lights, creating a different atmosphere compared to daytime rides.','Reddit (Skyline Luge Sentosa)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:58:15'),(117,234,'INSIDER','Remember your ticket/wristband for re-entry if you plan on doing multiple Luge rides. Losing it means you\'ll have to purchase another one.','Reddit (Skyline Luge Sentosa)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 17:58:15'),(118,235,'SAFETY','Beware of slippery surfaces! The snow and ice inside Snow City Singapore can be very slick. Wear appropriate footwear or utilize the provided boots carefully to prevent falls.','Reddit (Snow City Singapore)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 18:00:46'),(119,235,'SAFETY','Dress warmly in layers. Even with provided jackets, the sub-zero temperatures can be intense. Multiple layers will help you regulate your body temperature and enjoy your time without getting too cold, especially if you are not used to cold environments.','Reddit (Snow City Singapore)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 18:00:46'),(120,235,'SAFETY','Supervise children closely. The snowy environment can be disorienting, and children may wander off or encounter unexpected hazards like icy patches or snow-covered obstacles. Keep them within arm\'s reach at all times.','Reddit (Snow City Singapore)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 18:00:46'),(121,235,'SAFETY','Take breaks if you start feeling too cold. Don\'t push yourself to stay inside longer than you can comfortably handle. Head outside to warm up and then re-enter if you wish to continue enjoying the snow.','Reddit (Snow City Singapore)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 18:00:46'),(122,235,'SAFETY','Protect your eyes from the glare of the snow, especially on bright days. Sunglasses or goggles can help prevent snow blindness and ensure comfortable visibility inside Snow City Singapore.','Reddit (Snow City Singapore)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 18:00:46'),(123,235,'SAFETY','Be mindful of other visitors, particularly when using the snow slides or engaging in other activities. Avoid collisions and maintain a safe distance to prevent accidents.','Reddit (Snow City Singapore)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 18:00:46'),(124,235,'INSIDER','Go early! Beat the crowds for a less congested experience.','Reddit (Snow City Singapore)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 18:00:46'),(125,235,'INSIDER','Check for deals! Look for online discounts or package deals to save money on entry.','Reddit (Snow City Singapore)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 18:00:46'),(126,235,'INSIDER','Consider visiting during off-peak hours, weekdays or less popular times of the year will likely have shorter queues and a more relaxed atmosphere within Snow City Singapore.','Reddit (Snow City Singapore)','attraction',1,'2025-12-15 18:00:46'